Package: INWTUtils
Title: Utility functions used by INWT
Version: 1.0.1
Authors@R: c(person("Mira Celine", "Klein",
    email = "mira-klein@inwt-statistics.de", role = "cre"))
Maintainer: 'Mira Celine Klein' <mira-klein@inwt-statistics.de>
Description: This package provides several useful functions for the work with
    R projects and packages. There are helpful functions to create the file
	structure for a new project, functions to check the code style, and a
    function to ensure a clean working environment.
Depends:
    R (>= 3.3.2)
Imports:
    devtools (>= 1.13.2),
    dplyr (>= 0.7.0),
    lintr (>= 1.0.0),
    readr (>= 1.1.1)
